rows.label: tlk45600551_01_msg0001
rows.name:
This is a storage area for goods to be
transported into Alba Margen.

rows.label: tlk45600551_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Superbia's main exports are salvaged
materials and manufactured goods.

rows.label: tlk45600551_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Our food, though, is mostly imported.
Without the money our tech brings in,
we'd barely be able to feed ourselves.

rows.label: tlk45600551_01_msg0004
rows.name:
There's always a ton of imported
goods sitting around here, ready
to be carried into the city.

rows.label: tlk45600551_01_msg0005
rows.name:
The freight elevator needs permission
to use, but the personnel elevator is
open to the public.

rows.label: tlk45600551_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Now, you probably don't want to hang
around in a dusty old place like this.
Hurry along into the city.
